"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-uswnt-work-in-progress-win-mexico-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sophia Smith pulled back on her favorite right foot before letting off a lethal far-post shot from close range.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_Peletier\", \"score\": 0.9999999998472049, \"rank\": 1.5280042931113513e-10, \"text\": \"Sophia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_Peletier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophia_Peletier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ball cut through the humid New Jersey air before ricocheting against the back of the net, allowing the U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national team\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and the crowd at Red Bull Arena\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a sigh of relief.\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\", \"score\": 0.9999816533641475, \"rank\": 1.7828431631942325e-05, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey_Devils\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The breakthrough goal, coming in the 64th minute, proved to be the decider, securing the USWNT a 1\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00930 win over Mexico on Saturday.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999771338916154, \"rank\": 2.286663104628224e-05, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result was a perfectly respectable one against a formidable opponent, while also highlighting plenty of areas of improvement for Emma Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s young side ahead of the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s friendly was the first of two send-off matches for the USWNT before they head to the Summer Games.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFor the chances we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve created, we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not hitting the frame enough,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hayes said after the match.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s teaching them the right moments when to progress and when not to progress.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then in and around the penalty box, how to access the right spaces, in the right moments, in the right time.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to take a little bit of time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  The U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lone goal came from the familiar frontline duo of Smith and Mallory Swanson.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two, along with winger Trinity Rodman and attacking midfielder Rose Lavelle, played off each other with a palpable fluidity, creating a number of dangerous chances in the final third.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was really happy for Soph \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 I thought her and Mal were so dynamic,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hayes said.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trinity Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Lavelle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rose Lavelle\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Lavelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Lavelle\"}, {\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Reynolds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8609029919379836e-14, \"text\": \"Mal\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Reynolds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Reynolds\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd Trin got a little bit more space, but for me it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s execution, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what I will focus on.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Smith echoed her coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s statement, saying after the match that she wished she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d finished off a few more chances.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe cool thing about our attacking players is we can kind of all play all over the place, move around, be dynamic and if something feels right for someone in a different space, we can go into that space and others will fill,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith said.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1464, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trin\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe lost a little patience in the final third.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we get excited when we get in there, but maybe one touch too many, one pass too many.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Finishing has been a longstanding issue for the USWNT, with the squad only scoring four goals in four games during their ill-fated 2023 World Cup run.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hayes and her team hope some fine tuning and more time together will remedy any lingering scoring woes.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s match was the first outing since Hayes announced herOlympic roster, and came amid only her second camp with the USWNT.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve been together maybe total two weeks from last camp to this camp and it just feels like we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve learned and grown so much in those two weeks,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Lavelle said, adding that the team has been eagerly taking in knowledge from their new coach.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2635, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Lavelle\", \"score\": 0.9980927593273372, \"rank\": 0.0019108851906912392, \"text\": \"Lavelle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Lavelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Lavelle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hayes has been vocal about her mission to develop young talent, fostering the U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s emerging player pool while also keeping an eye on the fast-approaching Olympics.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s clear, however, that as much as the USWNT would like to improve upon their bronze-medal finish from the Tokyo Games, success now won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t come at the expense of sustainable growth for the future.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps, for that reason, it was important for Hayes to give young players opportunities, including Washington Spirit star Croix Bethune, who earned her first USWNT cap Saturday.\\u00c2  And as one player enjoyed her first appearance, another celebrated her 100th.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.564825417642517e-38, \"text\": \"Washington Spirit\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\"}, {\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.564825417642517e-38, \"text\": \"Washington Spirit\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\"}, {\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G._E._M._de_Ste._Croix\", \"score\": 0.9999447489219995, \"rank\": 5.525413095163376e-05, \"text\": \"Croix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G._E._M._de_Ste._Croix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G._E._M._de_Ste._Croix\"}, {\"begin\": 3229, \"end\": 3236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Bethune\", \"score\": 0.9999999999054126, \"rank\": 9.307617054514544e-11, \"text\": \"Bethune\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Bethune\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Bethune\"}, {\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team honored goalkeeper Alyssa Naeher\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 100th USWNT appearance before the game, bestowing her with a framed jersey for the occasion.\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about Naeher\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s impact on the squad, her teammates beamed, almost all of them heaping praise on the notoriously attention-averse 36-year-old.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI am obsessed with Alyssa,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith said.\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3676, \"end\": 3682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.999999874873091, \"rank\": 1.1003617491481483e-07, \"text\": \"Alyssa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe is amazing, I think everyone can say the same things about her.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is a leader in every way.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She shows up every single day with the best attitude.\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is such a selfless person.\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We see all the big saves she makes, and she is a hero in that way, but we all look up to her so much.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is the best teammate, the best friend, the best human.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Naeher wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t the only one to get her flowers.\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 1999 team\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094celebrating the 25th anniversary of its World Cup win\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094was also honored ahead of the match.\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A new USWNT era may be on the horizon under Hayes, but Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s match was something of a throwback, with \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009890s classics like Cher\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBelieve\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d bumping through Red Bull Arena to celebrate the squad.\", \"from\": 4208, \"to\": 4415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4214, \"end\": 4219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4377, \"end\": 4391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stadion_Wals-Siezenheim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9453323971287855e-29, \"text\": \"Red Bull Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stadion_Wals-Siezenheim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stadion_Wals-Siezenheim\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26,376 fans in attendance erupted for the likes of Mia Hamm and Brandi Chastain, who gathered at midfield ahead of the opening whistle.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI know right now we are in a moment where we are trying to rewrite our own narrative and have this team talk about itself, but I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t think we get to this unless we know our history and know our past and definitely the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009899ers were women who pushed the envelope and basically started this whole thing,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d forward Lynn Williams said.\", \"from\": 4416, \"to\": 4897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4471, \"end\": 4479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mia_Hamm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mia Hamm\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mia_Hamm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mia_Hamm\"}, {\"begin\": 4484, \"end\": 4499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandi_Chastain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brandi Chastain\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandi_Chastain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandi_Chastain\"}, {\"begin\": 4878, \"end\": 4891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lynn_Kanuka-Williams\", \"score\": 0.9960188057744004, \"rank\": 0.003997107450651844, \"text\": \"Lynn Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lynn_Kanuka-Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lynn_Kanuka-Williams\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAll the things we have right now [don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t] happen without them.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  The tribute was fitting given the current state of the team, now under a new head coach and looking to forge its own identity amid a generational shift.\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 5121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being in the midst of the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009899ers and reminded of the enduring legacy of the USWNT ahead of the Olympics seems to be a powerful form of motivation.\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5200, \"end\": 5205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s current group, there is still work to be done on the pitch.\", \"from\": 5271, \"to\": 5347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The squad showed flashes of what could be on Saturday, but, as the Olympics near, the USWNT is still a work in progress.\\u00c2  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5434, \"end\": 5439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_nationa